# Frontend (React)

- Mobile-first; no white screen; handle loading/error/empty states.
- Normal mode: no raw route quality/warnings/debug noise as primary content.
- Debug mode (`?debug=1`, `citygo.debug` in localStorage): show diagnostics, copy/send report.
- Match existing component patterns; Russian user-facing copy where applicable.
- Use shared debug helpers under `frontend/src/shared/debug/`.

## Tests

Vitest + Testing Library for visible behavior (normal + debug modes).  
`npm --prefix frontend test -- --run <file>`
